text: 9 January 2025 : Thursday Jan 2025 : Thursday Here are some fun rainbow aliens… I make probably 100+ new AI pictures (and a few videos) a day but I only publish less than 2%. Well let me restate that – that’s about 100 pictures I really like, but those come out of about 2000 total creations that I reject. I’m still using midjourney as my tool of choice.
html:
9

January 2025 : Thursday Jan 2025 : Thursday

Here are some fun rainbow aliens… I make probably 100+ new AI pictures (and a few videos) a day but I only publish less than 2%. Well let me restate that – that’s about 100 pictures I really like, but those come out of about 2000 total creations that I reject. I’m still using midjourney as my tool of choice.
